# Game-Collectors-Companion-Privacy-Policy

Privacy-relevant Android permissions requested by this app

CAMERA
Used for permissions that are associated with accessing camera or capturing images/video from the device.
This permission allows this application to use the CAMERA function of the phone to scan barcodes in order for barcodes to be stored to the local storage of the device. 

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE + android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.
Used for the base functionality of the app including data storage locally on the phone and sending data via e-mail. Data is not sent without user permission and only to the given address.

E-MAIL
Used only to send saved data to a given e-mail address and the address is not stored or used for marketing.
